## 🔄 Flujos Internos

### Inicio de Transferencia

```
POST /payments/transfer
        │
        ▼
PaymentController.transfer()
        │  @Valid TransferRequest + userId del JWT
        ▼
PaymentService.initiateTransfer()
        ├── Valida que sourceAccountId ≠ destinationAccountId
        ├── Consulta account-service via Feign: verifica que ambas cuentas existen y están ACTIVE
        ├── Llama a FraudDetectionService.evaluate()
        │       ├── Construye prompt con contexto de la transacción
        │       ├── Llama al modelo Spring AI
        │       └── Parsea FraudEvaluationResult
        │           └── Si riskScore >= threshold → FraudDetectedException (HTTP 422)
        ├── Persiste Transaction (status: PENDING, step: RESERVE_FUNDS)
        ├── Llama a SagaOrchestrator.start()
        │       └── PaymentEventPublisher.publishPaymentInitiated()
        │               → Kafka [payment.initiated]
        └── Retorna TransferResponse con transactionId y status PENDING
```

### Avance del Saga: Fondos Reservados

```
Kafka [account.funds-reserved]
        │
        ▼
PaymentEventConsumer.onFundsReserved()
        │
        ▼
SagaOrchestrator.onFundsReserved()
        ├── Actualiza Transaction: status → FUNDS_RESERVED, step → RECORD_LEDGER
        └── PaymentEventPublisher.publishPaymentCompleted()
                → Kafka [payment.completed]   ← ledger-service crea los asientos
```

### Avance del Saga: Asientos Registrados

```
Kafka [ledger.entries-recorded]
        │
        ▼
PaymentEventConsumer.onLedgerRecorded()
        │
        ▼
SagaOrchestrator.onLedgerRecorded()
        ├── Actualiza Transaction: status → COMPLETED, step → CONFIRM_PAYMENT
        └── Publica evento WebSocket → Frontend notifica al usuario ✅
```

### Compensación del Saga: Fondos no Reservados

```
Kafka [account.funds-reservation-failed]
        │
        ▼
PaymentEventConsumer.onFundsReservationFailed()
        │
        ▼
SagaOrchestrator.compensate()
        ├── Actualiza Transaction: status → FAILED, step → COMPENSATE, failureReason = reason
        └── Publica evento WebSocket → Frontend notifica al usuario ❌
        (no se publica payment.reversed porque nunca hubo fondos reservados)
```

### Compensación del Saga: Timeout de Ledger

```
Timeout en espera de [ledger.entries-recorded]
        │
        ▼
SagaOrchestrator.onTimeout()
        ├── Actualiza Transaction: status → REVERSED, step → COMPENSATE
        │   failureReason = "LEDGER_RECORDING_TIMEOUT"
        └── PaymentEventPublisher.publishPaymentReversed()
                → Kafka [payment.reversed]
                    ├── account-service libera la reserva de fondos
                    └── ledger-service registra asientos de compensación
```

---

*`payment-orchestrator` — Porque coordinar el movimiento de dinero requiere un director que conozca la partitura completa.*